1
00:00:17,140 --> 00:00:18,480
An Rao didn't take the pill,

2
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:20,519
yet she switched with me.

3
00:00:22,359 --> 00:00:23,079
Why?

4
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:24,280
The pill is inherently harmful.

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,140
Forcing the soul to switch

6
00:00:26,260 --> 00:00:27,179
is against the natural order.

7
00:00:27,879 --> 00:00:28,679
If frightened,

8
00:00:29,219 --> 00:00:30,219
one can switch

9
00:00:30,379 --> 00:00:31,239
without the pill.

10
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:32,679
If not for
the timely switch this time,

11
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:35,159
An Rao almost killed you.

12
00:00:36,820 --> 00:00:38,039
She is gentle and kind,

13
00:00:38,479 --> 00:00:39,560
and indeed only good at painting.

14
00:00:40,119 --> 00:00:41,500
But without her,

15
00:00:41,899 --> 00:00:42,340
we wouldn't

16
00:00:42,700 --> 00:00:44,280
have been able to enter the Treasure House.

17
00:00:46,079 --> 00:00:47,820
She is me, and I am her.

18
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:50,060
We share

19
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:51,560
life and death.

20
00:00:52,119 --> 00:00:52,719
Sister,

21
00:00:53,439 --> 00:00:54,820
Xie Huaiyun

22
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:55,899
has found our target
is the secret library.

23
00:00:57,740 --> 00:00:59,380
Why didn't he send more guards?

24
00:01:00,259 --> 00:01:02,140
Is it just because

25
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,240
he was addicted to drugs

26
00:01:03,619 --> 00:01:04,519
and couldn't take care of it?

27
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:08,739
I guess

28
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,359
the important thing

29
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,239
is either not in the secret library

30
00:01:12,859 --> 00:01:13,340
or

31
00:01:13,939 --> 00:01:15,700
is stored in a safe place.

32
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:18,719
Whether this is true

33
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,340
still needs to be verified.

34
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:23,480
This guy is quite tricky.

35
00:01:25,939 --> 00:01:27,519
Further probing is pointless.

36
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,239
Why not

37
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:34,959
just give him a big gift?

38
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,060
Since he fears fire,

39
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,359
let the fire

40
00:01:40,459 --> 00:01:42,379
start from the Treasure House.

41
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,019
My Lord,

42
00:01:44,620 --> 00:01:45,680
Xie Lingfeng has discovered

43
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,920
that you share a body with An Rao.

44
00:01:47,459 --> 00:01:48,519
If he uses this to threaten you,

45
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:49,480
I'm afraid...

46
00:02:01,180 --> 00:02:02,359
Did my lady instruct you?

47
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:04,900
At 11:45 PM,

48
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,780
set fire to the Treasure House.

49
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,240
She also gave me this.

50
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:17,840
No,

51
00:02:19,259 --> 00:02:20,840
I asked for this for you.

52
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:24,840
It's dangerous tonight.

53
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:27,419
I hope you can come back safely.

54
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,219
Although you have the same face,

55
00:02:38,419 --> 00:02:39,379
you are different.

56
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,419
The only one who can disturb me

57
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:43,159
is that madman.

58
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:43,939
Su Luoyao.

59
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,280
Thank you for your kindness.

60
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:46,900
But compared with me,

61
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,879
I hope you

62
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:50,039
take care of yourself.

63
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,080
and all the best.

64
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,479
It's getting late.

65
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:55,159
I'll take my leave.

66
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,280
General.

67
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:05,199
He actually told me

68
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,900
to take care of myself.

69
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:12,599
General.

70
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,020
Bai Zhen Order.

71
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,199
What can I do for you?

72
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,120
Lady An.
Please sit.

73
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:35,199
I was in a daze last night

74
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:36,879
and don't remember what happened.

75
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,879
I only vaguely recall...

76
00:03:39,099 --> 00:03:40,180
It was quite rude of me.

77
00:03:40,699 --> 00:03:41,639
I came to apologize.

78
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,699
Lady An, you have other guests.

79
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:51,800
What's this?

80
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,680
I accidentally poured an extra cup.

81
00:04:01,659 --> 00:04:02,879
And this talisman...

82
00:04:07,539 --> 00:04:08,039
This...

83
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,879
I asked for it for you.

84
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:15,379
Last night, you shared

85
00:04:15,379 --> 00:04:16,279
many stories with me.

86
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:19,040
May it bless you

87
00:04:19,379 --> 00:04:20,459
with peace and prosperity,

88
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,699
free from all worries.

89
00:04:23,899 --> 00:04:24,379
Anrao,

90
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:25,839
this is more precious than gold.

91
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,720
I will wear it every day,

92
00:04:27,939 --> 00:04:28,680
never parting from it.

93
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:37,439
With your heartfelt protection,

94
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:39,079
I fear nothing.

95
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,759
This night seems endless.

96
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,360
I'm starving.

97
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,699
I know, right?

98
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:18,920
Li!

99
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:21,560
Li!

100
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:24,319
Li!

101
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,459
Are you okay, Li?

102
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:32,680
Go, sister!

103
00:05:33,379 --> 00:05:34,040
Burn it all!

104
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,759
These filthy treasures of the Bureau.

105
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:04,680
These treasures

106
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,879
gathered from everywhere,

107
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:07,500
tonight,

108
00:06:08,139 --> 00:06:09,180
let's bid them farewell

109
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,600
with this fire.

110
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:17,220
[The warehouse is on fire!]

111
00:08:17,579 --> 00:08:18,860
[The warehouse is on fire!]

112
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,420
[The thieves have moved!]

113
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,120
[Someone, help!]

114
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:08,620
[The warehouse is on fire!]

115
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:09,840
[Fetch some water!]

116
00:09:09,860 --> 00:09:10,980
[Fire!]

117
00:09:11,059 --> 00:09:11,820
[Hurry!]

118
00:09:13,179 --> 00:09:13,980
[This way!]

119
00:09:14,139 --> 00:09:15,139
[Someone, help!]

120
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,240
[Fire!]

121
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,259
[Come on!]

122
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:19,600
[Hurry!]

123
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,100
[Bring some water!]

124
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:21,940
[On the way!]

125
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,779
Over there!

126
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,799
Within half an hour,

127
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:29,720
the fire must be put out!

128
00:09:33,379 --> 00:09:34,059
Bai Zhen!

129
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,200
You have failed my trust!

130
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:38,039
The fire in the warehouse

131
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,779
is your responsibility!

132
00:09:40,740 --> 00:09:41,840
The treasury has been burned down,

133
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,539
and I will investigate it myself!

134
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:44,960
The Xie family

135
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:46,919
must be feeling the pain now!

136
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,539
You're stripped of your position,

137
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:51,320
and fined for 3 years.

138
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:53,220
This is your punishment.

139
00:09:53,539 --> 00:09:54,080
Your Majesty,

140
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,440
there's something fishy about it.

141
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:57,899
I'm willing to find out the truth

142
00:09:58,159 --> 00:09:59,120
to redeem my fault.

143
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:01,039
Take him away.

144
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:02,899
[Prince of Lin'an is here.]

145
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:26,620
Sit.

146
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:28,179
Thank you, Your Majesty.

147
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,200
I heard about the fire at the Treasure House.

148
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:37,700
I came to check it out.

149
00:10:38,179 --> 00:10:39,059
Huaiyun is young,

150
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:40,419
and made mistakes.

151
00:10:40,899 --> 00:10:43,080
Please be lenient.

152
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:47,580
Why not let him make amends

153
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,580
by replenishing the shortfall?

154
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:52,659
The Treasure House holds priceless items.

155
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:53,960
How will we

156
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:56,139
replace those losses?

157
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:06,960
Father,

158
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,000
the treasury has suffered significant losses.

159
00:11:14,539 --> 00:11:17,379
The Bureau of Treasures collects rare items.

160
00:11:18,019 --> 00:11:19,480
The missing items

161
00:11:19,980 --> 00:11:21,960
must be replenished from the world.

162
00:11:23,059 --> 00:11:24,679
Now that the young emperor has ascended,

163
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,960
and the treasury is depleted,

164
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:27,960
the people

165
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:30,200
should contribute to the nation.

166
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:37,700
The people have endured droughts and floods,

167
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,879
and are suffering greatly.

168
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:40,840
How can I...

169
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:43,539
Serving the emperor is my duty.

170
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,360
The treasury is empty,

171
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:48,120
and it should be filled with the blood of the people.

172
00:11:48,399 --> 00:11:49,740
Even if the people are dying,

173
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:52,779
it's also worthwhile.

174
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,919
How absurd!

175
00:12:07,740 --> 00:12:09,080
Under the power,

176
00:12:09,659 --> 00:12:10,960
everyone is like a bird in a cage.

177
00:12:11,539 --> 00:12:12,679
Life and death

178
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:15,000
are all in the hands of these demons.

179
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:20,700
No!

180
00:12:21,139 --> 00:12:22,039
Let go of me!

181
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:23,720
Not to mention the fact that

182
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,279
he's surrounded by skilled fighters,
but with your abilities,

183
00:12:25,259 --> 00:12:26,399
you can't even get close to him!

184
00:12:26,899 --> 00:12:27,960
If you keep holding me back,

185
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,220
I'll kill you too!

186
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,240
As long as I'm alive,

187
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:32,820
I won't let you throw your life away!

188
00:12:37,779 --> 00:12:38,720
According to the Five Ghosts,

189
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:39,980
the secret from back then

190
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,539
should be in this box.

191
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:47,600
Bloodthirsty smoke...
